# RenovaBit Landing — Project Rules

## Stack & Tooling
- Framework: **Astro 7** | UI: **Preact 10** | Styling: **Tailwind CSS v4** (@tailwindcss/vite)
- Icons: **astro-icon + @iconify-json/hugeicons** (`<Icon name="hugeicons:icon-name" />`)
- Linting/Formatting: **Biome 2.4** (standalone, root: true) — NO Prettier, NO ESLint
- Package Manager: **Bun** — NO npm/yarn/pnpm
- TypeScript: strict mode, `verbatimModuleSyntax: true`, path alias `@/*` → `./src/*`

## Scripts
- `bun dev` → astro dev :3000 | `bun build` | `bun preview` | `bun check` (astro) | `bun check:biome`

## Commits (Conventional Commits)
- `<type>(<scope>): <message>` — types: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|build|ci|chore|revert
- Scopes: ui|seo|content|a11y|perf|deps|ci|repo — max 72 chars, imperative, lowercase, no period

## Conventions
- **Biome** runs pre-commit (staged files), commitlint checks message, pre-push checks all.
- **Tailwind v4 only** — NO tailwind.config.js, NO @apply, NO postcss plugin. Use `@import "tailwindcss"`.
- **compressHTML: true** — traditional whitespace (not JSX mode).
- **Components**: PascalCase (.astro or .tsx). Directories: kebab-case. Assets: kebab-case.
- **Form inputs**: label ABOVE, helper text optional, error text BELOW. NO placeholder-as-label.
- **Layout**: `min-h-[100dvh]` not `h-screen`. Grid over flex percentage-math.
- **Animations**: only `transform` + `opacity`. Custom cubic-beziers. Honor `prefers-reduced-motion`.
- **No window scroll listeners** — use IntersectionObserver or `whileInView`.

## Fonts
- **Inter** → body text, UI elements, paragraphs, nav
- **Manrope** → headings, titles, hero display
- Fonts loaded via Astro Fonts API (`fontProviders.local()`) — self-hosted, preloaded

## Anti-patterns (banned)
- AI-purple gradients, 3-equal-feature-cards, harsh shadows
- Em-dashes (`—`) anywhere visible
- Hand-rolled SVG icons or decorative SVGs
- Div-based fake screenshots
- Lucide icons (unless explicitly requested)
- FontAwesome or Material Icons (use Hugeicons)
